channel.title: Using mangOH with Octave? Learn What's New in Octave
channel.description:
Hi everyone!
If you are using mangOH Red or Yellow with Octave edge-to-cloud plaftorm (or willing to do so), join us for a 1h live session to learn about new features in Octave (presentation, live demo, Q&A session).
Dec-3 2020, 17:00 CET / 11:00 EST / 8:00 PST **Jan-14 2021, 17:00 CET / 11:00 EST / 8:00 PST**
https://www.eventbrite.com/e/octave-whats-new-developer-session-registration-130015015411?aff=mangohforum
